               <img alt="career acceleration" class="media-element file-default" data-delta="41" height="800" src="https://accelerate.uoregon.edu/sites/accelerate2.uoregon.edu/files/resize/rs_kc_internship_program_145-scr-1187x800.jpg" typeof="foaf:Image" width="1187"/>
              </p>
             </div>
             <div class="envelope-feature__content">
              <div class="envelope-feature__content__title">
               Career Acceleration
              </div>
              <div class="envelope-feature__content__body">
               <p>
                The Knight Campus will provide cutting-edge professional development and training for students.
               </p>
               <p>
                <a class="cta-button" href="/career-acceleration">
                 Find out More
                </a>
               </p>
              </div>
