          <div class="envelope envelope--standard envelope--style-white" style="">
           <div class="section-header section-header--brown">
            <div class="section-header__title">
             <p>
              OHSU and UO partnership
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
           <div class="grid grid--2col-60-40">
            <div class="grid__item">
             <p>
              To further catalyze discovery and scientific impact, senior leaders at OHSU and UO are leading efforts to increase partnerships among faculty at both institutions. Three areas are currently being explored: research collaborations, educational programs, and administrative policies.
             </p>
             <p>
              <a class="cta-button cta-button--standard text--lowercase" href="http://blogs.uoregon.edu/ohsuuopartnership/">
               Explore the Partnership
              </a>
             </p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid__item">
             <img alt="Knight Campus meeting" class="media-element file-default" data-delta="25" height="488" src="https://accelerate.uoregon.edu/sites/accelerate2.uoregon.edu/files/knight_campus_meet_2_ato_cropped-2kh0kb6.png" typeof="foaf:Image" width="1000"/>
            </div>
